byline.contributor: David M. Herszenhorn contributed reporting from Moscow.

abstract: Fighting in Ukraine continues as cease-fire talks resume.
lead_paragraph: Envoys representing Ukraine, Russia and a European monitoring group opened a new round of cease-fire talks in Belarus on Saturday, but without leaders of the Russian-backed separatists.
